1. Users
    -> company
    -> expert
2. Jobs
    -> company
    -> title
    -> description
    -> list of requirements
    -> list of skills
    -> salary range
    -> type : remote / on-site / hybrid
    -> location
    -> languages
    -> expected start date (NULLABLE)
3. Expert
    -> name
    -> gender (2 options)
    -> profile pic
    -> work experience
    -> skills
    -> education
    -> status (looking / invisible)
    -> known languages
4. Application
    -> company
    -> candidate
    -> date